     F** AB#R487 *******************************************
     F*  MASTER MIXED PALLET LIST FOR TTTX (3511)          *
     F*  (BREAK BY INV#/SBAN/MHIN                          *
     F*  JW     2019.10.17                                 *
     F******************************************************
     FABWPP31 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAB#PP85 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAB#PR487O   E             70     PRINTER
     E*-----------------------------------------------------
     E                    WW          4  1
     E                    T1          5  1
     E                    T2         11  1
     E*-----------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1  20 IMHN
